---
/* Componente: Cómo Empezar - BeTogether */
---

<section class="pt-24 pb-10 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900" id="como-empezar">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-center mb-20 uppercase dark:text-white">
      Cómo <span class="text-primary tracking-tighter">Empezar</span>
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 relative">
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-1/4 right-1/4 h-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-800 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-3xl font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-white">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 dark:text-white">Regístrate Ahora</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Regístrate en nuestro programa pionero en menos de 2 minutos. Sin cargos ocultos.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-800 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-brand-blue group-hover:text-primary transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-3xl font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-primary">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 dark:text-white">Promociona Productos</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Escoge entre diferentes  plantillas y usa  herramientas como : control de inventarios, logistica, ventas, genera piezas con IA  y mas!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-800 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-green-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="text-3xl font-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-white">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 dark:text-white">Gana y Escala</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Recibe pagos semanales y sube en el ranking para convertirte en un Afiliado Estrella.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>